    "body": "For the case of #845, I can \"update\" the configuration of the **hits** widget by overriding it (add a new widget in the same container), but with another template.\n\nThen, I call `search.start()`.\nIt works with little side effects (for the moment, I only have a problem with one other widget. See #845 for more information).\n\nI don't know if it helps or not because I don't know your lib at all, but I have the feeling it's not far from already working.\n",
